reviews.review_text: Phenomenal West LA is monumental. The more I reflect on the Grateful Dead they were really in a unique zone. All of the coat tail bands are not even within the same solar system as the Grateful Dead with Garcia. Write your own music if you want to enter the Coliseum of Greatness!
